				BaseColor.rgb * PrimaryDetailColor.rgb * 
				SecondaryDetailColor.rgb * MicroDetailColor.rgb * BumpColor.rgb *
				(Ambient + DistantLight0Diffuse + DistantLight1Diffuse), 
				0.0f, 1.0f
			), BumpColor.w);
		} else {
